          </article>

          <article class="vehicle-card">
            <div class="image-container">
              <span class="vehicle-badge">Adventure Van</span>
              <img src="/images/vehicles/survan-tn.jpg" alt="2020 Custom Surf Van in blue and white" class="vehicle-image">
            </div>

            <div class="vehicle-info">
              <div class="vehicle-header">
                <h2 class="vehicle-title">2020 Custom Surf Van</h2>
